            Resolution 30-90 minutes:
            11. Fix: Apply correction
            12. Test: Dev environment first
            13. Deploy: To production
            14. Rerun: Failed job with backfill
            15. Monitor: Job completion

            Validation 90-120 minutes:
            16. Data quality: Run checks
            17. Row count: Verify expected
            18. Downstream: Check dependent jobs
            19. Dashboards: Verify data updated
            20. Close: Incident resolved

            Prevention:
            - Add: Data quality checks
            - Update: Error handling
            - Improve: Monitoring alerts
